desc:
Int32x4 and operations.

Int32x4 stores 4 32-bit bit-masks in "lanes". The lanes are "x", "y", "z", and "w" respectively.
name: dart:typed_data.Int32x4

methods.example:
Implementation

external factory Int32x4(int x, int y, int z, int w);
methods.name: Int32x4

methods.desc: Merge trueValue and falseValue based on this' bit mask: Select bit from trueValue when bit in this is on. Select bit from falseValue when bit in this is off.
methods.example:
Implementation

Float32x4 select(Float32x4 trueValue, Float32x4 falseValue);
methods.name: select

methods.desc: Shuffle the lane values. mask must be one of the 256 shuffle constants.
methods.name: shuffle

methods.desc: Shuffle the lane values in this and other. The returned Int32x4 will have XY lanes from this and ZW lanes from other. Uses the same mask as shuffle.
methods.example:
Implementation

Int32x4 shuffleMix(Int32x4 other, int mask);
methods.name: shuffleMix
